00:09:35.510 --> 00:09:37.120
amid your busy schedule

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.000
to accompany me

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.360
to this important competition?

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:40.600
The busy President Ye

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.550
prioritizes her career, of course.

00:09:42.550 --> 00:09:44.810
You focus on your competition tomorrow.

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:47.240
The view up there looks nice.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.640
Let's go check it out.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:50.630
Didn't you come

00:09:50.630 --> 00:09:52.630
to accompany me to the competition?

00:09:52.870 --> 00:09:54.670
Why are you busy with work again?

00:10:02.790 --> 00:10:03.390
Haimeng.

00:10:03.790 --> 00:10:04.390
Haimeng?

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:05.320
Haimeng!

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:06.630
Haimeng!

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:08.840
Haimeng!

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:11.200
A pretty young lady

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:12.270
just ran up there.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:14.080
Thank you.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:15.630
Haimeng!

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:18.870
Young man,

00:10:18.870 --> 00:10:20.960
wish you a victorious start tomorrow.

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:21.630
Me?

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:26.200
Thank you.

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:26.750
Bye bye.

00:10:30.630 --> 00:10:31.600
Handsome guy,

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:35.040
may you win the championship
with a single shot tomorrow.

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:40.440
Handsome boy,

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:42.700
tomorrow's champion will surely be you.

00:11:16.060 --> 00:11:17.370
♪ I'll be the wind for you ♪

00:11:18.220 --> 00:11:19.560
♪ Elusive and unsure ♪

00:11:19.940 --> 00:11:23.390
♪ I'll cross through seasons
to embrace you ♪

00:11:24.140 --> 00:11:25.200
♪ I'll be the rain for you ♪

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.080
Tomorrow,

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:26.240
I'll be with you from your first arrow

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:27.670
♪ In the barren stretch of time ♪

00:11:28.090 --> 00:11:28.270
♪ Watering two lonely souls ♪

00:11:28.270 --> 00:11:29.200
all the way

00:11:29.550 --> 00:11:31.350
until you win the championship.

