00:11:35.620 --> 00:11:35.720
♪ Only wanting to stay ♪

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:37.090
nor do you need
to prove anything to anyone.

00:11:37.090 --> 00:11:37.870
♪ And guard your little isle ♪

00:11:37.870 --> 00:11:38.510
Just move

00:11:38.510 --> 00:11:39.410
toward the direction you want to go

00:11:39.410 --> 00:11:40.910
♪ Finally, I turn into ♪

00:11:41.150 --> 00:11:41.440
and do your best.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:42.930
♪ The warm glow of daily life ♪

00:11:43.670 --> 00:11:44.480
♪ To brighten the meaning of life ♪

00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:45.200
Okay.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:47.700
I will.

00:11:47.700 --> 00:11:49.200
♪ I'll be a childhood shooting star ♪

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:49.840
Now,

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.390
close your eyes.

00:11:51.610 --> 00:11:54.930
♪ To stay through every dawn with you ♪

00:11:55.700 --> 00:11:57.510
♪ Crossing years, crossing uneasy fate ♪

00:11:57.510 --> 00:11:58.200
Three.

00:11:59.160 --> 00:11:59.320
♪ Turn into a ring
to hold your life tight ♪

00:11:59.320 --> 00:11:59.840
Two.

