Did you prepare all this specially?

00:12:11.790 --> 00:12:11.830
Coming to Xiamen,

00:12:11.830 --> 00:12:13.250
♪ Turning mountains and seas ♪

00:12:13.550 --> 00:12:13.840
♪ Into the most beautiful verses ♪

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:14.870
I didn't expect you to prepare

00:12:14.870 --> 00:12:16.070
such a surprise for me.

00:12:16.070 --> 00:12:16.750
♪ With your name signed at the end ♪

00:12:16.750 --> 00:12:18.270
I prepared a surprise for you too.

00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:19.000
♪ Only you ♪

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:19.750
I want

00:12:20.030 --> 00:12:20.170
to create

00:12:20.170 --> 00:12:23.000
♪ I'll rush to you
in place of all things ♪

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:24.200
the most beautiful memories here

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:25.720
♪ I'll sink into your heart
in place of fallen leaves ♪

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:27.270
with the person I love most.

00:12:27.840 --> 00:12:31.500
♪ The wind never stops,
