00:14:05.960 --> 00:14:07.150
Are you trying

00:14:07.840 --> 00:14:09.150
to get me killed with this,

00:14:09.150 --> 00:14:10.270
or drag the entire Ye family down

00:14:10.270 --> 00:14:11.200
with you?

